# Claude Code git worktrees — machine-local scratch checkouts that each carry
# their own biome.json (a nested root config). Ignoring them keeps `git status`
# clean and stops `biome ci .` from tripping over the nested config (Biome honors
# .gitignore via vcs.useIgnoreFile). Tracked files elsewhere under .claude/ (e.g.
# skills) are unaffected.
.claude/worktrees/

# The repository-root .gitignore has a broad `lib/` rule (for build output) that
# unintentionally matches this React source directory. Re-include it so the
# client source is tracked.
!client/src/lib/
!client/src/lib/**
